==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nolo contendere
<hw>No"lo con*ten"de*re</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[L., I do not wish
to contend.]</ety> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>A plea, by the defendant, in a
criminal prosecution, which, without admitting guilt, subjects him to
all the consequences of a plea of guilty.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nol. pros.</ent>⟦br⟧
